name: Secret Lodge Buyan Lake
address: Jl. Tut Ardi, Pancasari, Kec. Sukasada, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81161, Indonesia
review 1:
I would give more stars if I could!

This experience was incredibly rejuvenating. The lodge has a homely and warm feel! The hosts are incredibly talented and professional, thinking of all sorts of little things throughout my stay that improved it! From bringing out a throw blanket when I was reading in the evening to surprising me with gluten free crepes it was these small touches that made my stay!

I loved every single mouthful of the delicious meals and desserts. The massage I ordered was high quality! My room was relaxing and had everything I needed!

Truly deserves these 5 stars and I can see why other gave them too!

review 3:
Lovely place and host , located on top of the hill facing the lake. The house is fully furnish and all equipped with all you need.

review 4:

review 5: We were so happy with our stay! Stephanie, Ludo, and their daughter were more than accommodating and so nice to talk to. All the food was delicious!!
